se-sous-licence-mit-bootstrap-et-jquery-mis-a-jour.htm" rel="nofollow">&laquo;&nbsp;<cite style="font-style: normal;">HTML5 Boilerplate passe sous licence MIT, Bootstrap et JQuery mis &agrave; jour</cite>&nbsp;&raquo;</a><small class="cachelinks">&nbsp;[<a title="archive sur Wikiwix" href="http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcinpact.com%2Fnews%2F73484-html5-boilerplate-passe-sous-licence-mit-bootstrap-et-jquery-mis-a-jour.htm">archive</a>]</small>, PC INpact,&lrm; <time class="nowrap" datetime="2012-08-31">31 ao&ucirc;t 2012</time> <small style="line-height: 1em;">(consult&eacute; le <span class="nowrap">20 mars 2014</span>)</small></span>.</span></li>\r\n<li id="cite_note-zdnet-6"><span class="noprint renvois_vers_le_texte">&uarr; <sup><a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bootstrap_%28framework%29#cite_ref-zdnet_6-0">a</a> et <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bootstrap_%28framework%29#cite_ref-zdnet_6-1">b</a></sup></span> <span class="reference-text"><span id="2011" class="ouvrage"><span class="indicateur-langue">(<abbr class="abbr" title="Langue&nbsp;: anglais">en</abbr>)</span> <a class="external text" href="http://www.zdnet.com/blog/btl/twitter-rolls-out-bootstrap-toolkit-for-developing-web-apps/55576" rel="nofollow">&laquo;&nbsp;<cite style="font-style: normal;">Twitter rolls out Bootstrap toolkit for developing web apps</cite>&nbsp;&raquo;</a><small class="cachelinks">&nbsp;[<a title="archive sur Wikiwix" href="http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zdnet.com%2Fblog%2Fbtl%2Ftwitter-rolls-out-bootstrap-toolkit-for-developing-web-apps%2F55576">archive</a>]</small>, zdnet.com,&lrm; <time class="nowrap" datetime="2011-08-19">19 ao&ucirc;t 2011</time> <small style="line-height: 1em;">(consult&eacute; le <span class="nowrap">20 mars 2014</span>)</small></span>.</span></li>\r\n<li id="cite_note-7"><span class="noprint renvois_vers_le_texte"><a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bootstrap_%28framework%29#cite_ref-7">&uarr;</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage"><span class="indicateur-langue">(<abbr class="abbr" title="Langue&nbsp;: anglais">en</abbr>)</span> <a class="external text" href="http://dojobootstrap.com/" rel="nofollow">&laquo;&nbsp;<cite style="font-style: normal;">Dojo Bootstrap</cite>&nbsp;&raquo;</a><small class="cachelinks">&nbsp;[<a title="archive sur Wikiwix" href="http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdojobootstrap.com%2F">archive</a>]</small> <small style="line-height: 1em;">(consult&eacute; le <span class="nowrap">15 avril 2014</span>)</small></span>.</span></li>\r\n<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="noprint renvois_vers_le_texte"><a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bootstrap_%28framework%29#cite_ref-8">&uarr;</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage"><span class="indicateur-langue">(<abbr class="abbr" title="Langue&nbsp;: anglais">en</abbr>)</span> <a class="external text" href="http://angular-ui.github.io/bootstrap/" rel="nofollow">&laquo;&nbsp;<cite style="font-style: normal;">UI Bootstrap</cite>&nbsp;&raquo;</a><small class="cachelinks">&nbsp;[<a title="archive sur Wikiwix" href="http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fangular-ui.github.io%2Fbootstrap%2F">archive</a>]</small> <small style="line-height: 1em;">(consult&eacute; le <span class="nowrap">15 avril 2014</span>)</small></span>.</span></li>\r\n<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="noprint renvois_vers_le_texte"><a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bootstrap_%28framework%29#cite_ref-9">&uarr;</a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage"><span class="indicateur-langue">(<abbr class="abbr" title="Langue&nbsp;: anglais">en</abbr>)</span> <a class="external text" href="http://mgcrea.github.io/angular-strap/" rel="nofollow">&laquo;&nbsp;<cite style="font-style: normal;">AngularStrap</cite>&nbsp;&raquo;</a><small class="cachelinks">&nbsp;[<a title="archive sur Wikiwix" href="http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmgcrea.github.io%2Fangular-strap%2F">archive</a>]</small> <small style="line-height: 1em;">(consult&eacute; le <span class="nowrap">15 avril 2014</span>)</small></span>.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><span id="Voir_aussi" class="mw-headline">Voir aussi</span></h2>\r\n<h3><span id="Articles_connexes" class="mw-headline">Articles connexes</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a title="Framework d''interface" href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Framework_d%27interface">Framework d''interface</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><span id="Liens_externes" class="mw-headline">Liens externes</span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><cite id="site_officiel" class="ouvrage"><span style="font-style: normal;"><span class="indicateur-langue">(<abbr class="abbr" title="Langue&nbsp;: anglais">en</abbr>)</span> <a class="external text" href="http://getbootstrap.com/" rel="nofollow">Site officiel</a><small class="cachelinks">&nbsp;[<a title="archive sur Wikiwix" href="http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgetbootstrap.com%2F">archive</a>]</small></span></cite></li>\r\n<li><a class="external text" href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap" rel="nofollow">Le projet Bootstrap sur GitHub</a><small class="cachelinks">&nbsp;[<a title="archive sur Wikiwix" href="http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ftwbs%2Fbootstrap">archive</a>]</small></li>\r\n<li><a class="external text" href="http://www.superkraft.fr/bootstrap-basictemplates/" rel="nofollow">Explication du syst&egrave;me de grille de Bootstrap</a><small class="cachelinks">&nbsp;[<a title="archive sur Wikiwix" href="http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.superkraft.fr%2Fbootstrap-basictemplates%2F">archive</a>]</small></li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>Tweety le petit oisal.</p>', 4, 'Bootstrap, Twitter, Framework, CSS, Stylesheet', 0, '2016-12-24 17:05:24', NULL, 3, 1);

